          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "collapsible_text": "Shipping & Return",
            "collapsible_liquid": "<div class=\"shipping-return\">\n<p><strong>Shipping</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Processing time:</strong> 1–3 business days.</li>\n<li><strong>Delivery Time:</strong> 5–12 business days for standard items.</li>\n<li><strong>Free US Shipping:</strong> All orders include fast, local dispatch from US warehouses via FedEx, DHL, CEVA, and UPS.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>All orders are tracked online and delivered in discreet and impact-proof packaging.</p>\n<p><em>Tips: If the product is too large, it will be shipped in 2–3 courier waybills. Avoid squeezing and damage during transportation.</em></p>\n<p><a href=\"/policies/shipping-policy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"color: #1a73e8;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><u>Learn more Shipping Policy</u></span></span></a><a href=\"/pages/shipping-policy\" style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #1a73e8;\"></a></p>\n<p><strong>30-Day Return &amp; Refund</strong></p>\n<p>To initiate a return, please contact: <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 170, 255); text-decoration: underline;\">service@mindyes.shop</span></span></p>\n<p><a href=\"/policies/refund-policy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"color: #1a73e8;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><u>Learn more refunds &amp; returns</u></span></span></a></p>\n</div>",
            "collapsible_content": ""
          }
        },
