        "collapsible_UkJdgF": {
          "type": "collapsible",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "collapsible_text": "Shop With Confidence",
            "collapsible_liquid": "",
            "collapsible_content": "<p><strong>- SAFE PAYMENTS</strong><br/>With global payment options, your payment at AuricAdorn is secure and fast.<br/><br/><strong>- LOGISTICS GUARANTEE</strong><br/>1. Provide accurate online logistics tracking services for each parcel!<br/><br/><strong>- SECURITY & PRIVACY</strong><br/>Protecting your privacy is IMPORTANT to us! We DO NOT sell your personal information and your information will only be in accordance with our privacy policy in order to improve better service.<br/><a href=\"/policies/privacy-policy\" title=\"Privacy Policy\">Learn more about our Privacy Policy.</a><br/><br/><strong>- CUSTOMER SERVICE</strong><br/>Our customer service is always here, and we look forward to hearing from you! Contact via <a href=\"mailto:yjivggqjo@126.com\" title=\"mailto:yjivggqjo@126.com\">support@auricadorn.com</a>. we will be with you very soon!<br/><br/><strong>Return Refund Policy</strong><br/>If your order has been processed, we will provide return and refund services under the following conditions:<br/>1. If you want to return the product, please contact our customer service within 30 days after receiving the package (determine the arrival date based on the tracking information).<br/>2. All items must be unworn, in original condition, with original packaging and all tags.<br/>3. Damaged or wrong item received (Please check your order when you receive the item. If the item is defective, damaged or you received the wrong item, please contact us immediately so that we can evaluate the problem and correct it. We will resend the correct product or refund you unconditionally)<br/><a href=\"/policies/refund-policy\" title=\"Refund Policy\">Learn more refunds & returns</a></p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_eaDjfy": {
          "type": "collapsible",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "collapsible_text": "Description",
            "collapsible_liquid": "<div class=\"product-detail-box\">{{ product.description }}</div>",
            "collapsible_content": "<p><strong>【Compact 1-Person Indoor Sauna】</strong><br/>The Outexer HY1 infrared sauna measures 33\" x 28\" x 62\", perfectly sized for solo relaxation at home. Designed for indoor use, it features a towel rack and tempered glass for added style. Whether in your master bathroom, bedroom, basement, or gym—enjoy the luxury of an Outexer sauna in your own space, with a max temperature of 149°F.</p><p><strong>【Premium Canadian Hemlock & Entertainment System】</strong><br/>Crafted from natural Canadian Hemlock, this indoor sauna is durable, beautiful, and heat-efficient. Equipped with an advanced entertainment system and two premium speakers, the 980W heating system reaches optimal temperature in just 30 minutes, delivering soothing warmth and immersive comfort.</p><p><strong>【Far Infrared Wellness Benefits】</strong><br/>Enjoy full-body rejuvenation from Outexer far infrared sauna therapy. From improving circulation and skin tone to relieving muscle fatigue and promoting better sleep, this spa room supports both physical and mental wellness. An integrated oxygen bar adds to the health benefits—just relax and let the heat do the work.</p><p><strong>【Smart Controls & Safety Features】</strong><br/>Easily control time and temperature using the digital panel. Safety-first design includes dry burn protection, explosion-proof systems, automatic power-off, leak prevention, and ultra low-EMF infrared carbon panels that wrap your body in safe, consistent heat.</p><p><strong>【Reliable Support & Easy Maintenance】</strong><br/>As a trusted infrared sauna company, Outexer® offers full post-purchase support with 24/7 engineer service. Setup is simple, and the seat and foot grid are coated with non-toxic water-based paint. After use, just wipe clean with a towel—ready for your next personal sauna escape.</p>"
          }
