    "product_experience_E3CyAF": {
      "type": "product-experience",
      "blocks": {
        "text_pQdKDe": {
          "type": "text",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "item_title": "Complimentary Shipping & Returns",
            "item_info": "<p>Free standard shipping on all orders(via ePacket/ PostalParcel).<br/>$8.90 express shipping 8-15 days via USPS/ UPSWWE.<br/>All orders are tracked online and delivered in discreet and impact-proof packaging.<br/>30-Day Free Return & Refund-To initiate a return, please contact us.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_tpzhwL": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "item_title": "Jewelry Design",
            "item_info": "<p>Each of our jewelry is carefully designed and unique, keeping up with the trends of world-renowned brands while maintaining our own unique design. Our goal is to surpass our competitors.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_QQqYPc": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "item_title": "Packing Box",
            "item_info": "<p>For each piece of jewelry you purchase from us, we will prepare an exquisite gift box for it. Whether you buy it for yourself or as a gift for others, the beautiful gift box can give people a very considerate feeling. Meanwhile, good packaging can also protect the jewelry very well.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_n9hfeJ": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "item_title": "Size Guide",
            "item_info": "<p>Jewelry is a wonderful way to express yourself, but the right size is key. This guide focuses on the proper sizing for bracelets, rings, and necklaces. Read on to helping you understand the dimensional parameters and measurement methods.<br/><a href=\"/pages/size-guide\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Size Guide\">Learn more...</a></p>"
          }
        },
        "text_jNj8Kh": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "item_title": "Product Craftsmanship",
            "item_info": "<p>We use extremely high-quality raw materials to bring excellent quality to every piece of jewelry. After multiple processes of polishing, the details are made even better, allowing each piece of jewelry to radiate its unique delicacy and beauty.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_FJgWnj": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "item_title": "Competitive Price",
            "item_info": "<p>Our products are meticulously designed and of outstanding quality, yet our prices remain unrivaled. For the same level of quality, our prices are more favorable. Welcome to join us.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_GPx68n": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "item_title": "Environmental Protection Concept",
            "item_info": "<p>AuricAdorn adheres to the concepts of putting people first and protecting the environment. We attach great importance to the responsibility of environmental protection in aspects such as production and packaging, and try our best to use recyclable raw materials. In line with the principle of avoiding waste while not cutting corners, we bring everyone high-quality jewelry.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
